{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-work-template-js","path":"/vodafone/","result":{"data":{"page":{"id":"10e231e2-8ab1-5cb6-a2c6-81055c8e3b63","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/39bda915162c854896f3c918b4e1a6c8/dbdff/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/39bda915162c854896f3c918b4e1a6c8/dbdff/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/39bda915162c854896f3c918b4e1a6c8/d1f95/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/39bda915162c854896f3c918b4e1a6c8/dbdff/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>While working at Vodafone, I was tasked to do an interactive data visualisation piece for one of its clients.</p>\n<p>The idea was to show a world map with a timeline to represent the mobile calls of a particular subscriber of the client. The calls were represented with particles jumping from the origin of the call to the destination.</p>\n<p>To amplify the visual appeal of the animation, I used a few Javascript libraries and APIs to represent the particles and their trails in the map:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Leaflet/Leaflet.fullscreen\">leaflet full-screen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Leaflet/Leaflet.markercluster\">leaflet markercluster</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/domoritz/leaflet-locatecontrol\">leaflet locatecontrol</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.mapbox.com/mapbox.js/api/v3.1.1/\">mapbox</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/artzub/blackhole.js\">blackhole.js</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://d3js.org/\">d3.js</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"prefix":"2017"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Vodafone","categories":"vodafone web inverted leaflet mapbox blackhole d3","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/fc71b09d1df391daf9e7a50d1d0ccf32/f3583/logo.png"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/vodafone/","source":"work"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}